data.description: Absolutely charming and move-in-ready! Welcome to this ranch style home where comfort meets convenience. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious living area that invites you to relax and unwind. The main floor hosts two cozy bedrooms, offering ample space for your personal retreat. But the real treasure lies on the lower level, with a third bedroom, family room, laundry room and a walk out basement entry. Plus, the front view of the woods adds a touch of serenity to your daily life, providing a perfect blend of nature and suburban living. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make 1487 Second St your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm, versatility, and convenience of this lovely property. Your dream home awaits!
